  "text": "One can expect very strong nonlinear effects from microcavity polaritons due to the strong interaction of the cavity mode with the quantum well exciton [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We point out that there is no comparable one-photon excitation experiment-such an experiment will not work because the exciting laser will be reflected directly back into the imaging system.",
